 monthly.<\/p>\n<p>If you think your pet may be suffering from arthritis or <em>slowing down<\/em>, come and see us!\u00a0 We will discuss the best plan to keep this painful condition at bay!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Arthritis Is your pet &#8220;slowing down&#8221;? This is likely arthritis! Every animal will develop arthritis. It is a painful and depressing condition that is commonly mistaken by owners as slowing down. What are signs of arthritis or slowing down? One or all of: &#8211; Difficult standing from a sitting position &#8211; Getting skinny back legs &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/arthritis\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Arthritis<\/span> Read More &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/726"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=726"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/726\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1006,"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/726\/revisions\/1006"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/dev.ivanhoeeastvet.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=726"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}